NURSE-SEX (Scottsdale, Ariz.) _ A husband-wife nurse team fired
Thursday by a Scottsdale hospital for running an X-rated Web site
aren't giving up their business, they're expanding. George Miller
says he's posted suggestive pictures of his wife, Tracy, in her
role as ``the very touchable Dakota Rae'' on 250 free X-rated Web
sites every day since the couple were suspended July 1 by
Scottsdale Healthcare Osborn. By MIKE CRISSEY. Story will move in
