<TEXT>
<P>
   HALIFAX, NOVA SCOTIA _ First passive smoking, now passive
smelling.
</P>
<P>
   It cannot be tolerated, the people of Halifax, the capital of
Nova Scotia, are being told. Though the air in this Canadian port
may sometimes carry the fragrance of fish, the citizens themselves
