<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-06 03:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7841 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RECOGNIZE-SOMALILAND?     08-06 1114
