   SEVENTEEN-HOUSTON (Undated) _ Seventeen magazine names Houston
as one of top 10 U.S. cities for teen-agers. The others are Ann
Arbor, Mich.; Billings, Mont.; Boston; Boulder, Colo.; Honolulu;
Montclair, N.J.; New York; San Francisco and Seattle. San Francisco
was singled out as the top town for teens, but the other nine
weren't ranked. By JEANNIE KEVER.
