   COMPUTER-COLUMN (Undated) _ It's fitting that one of the most
popular items people use their computers to buy over the Internet
is ... other computers. There's something wonderfully circular
about updating your compu-clunker with a few clicks of its mouse,
and having a shiny new replacement show up on your doorstep a few
days later. An example of three PCs you can buy online. By DWIGHT
