<HEADER>
A8084 &Cx1f; tab-z
r f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-DAY-TRADING-SUCKERS-N     08-06 0842
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-DAY-TRADING-SUCKERS-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
DAY TRADING IS FOR SUCKERS
</HEADLINE>
  (Slate commentary)  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; By JAMES SUROWIECKI &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) &LR;  &QC;
