<DOCNO> NYT19990806.0115 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-06 13:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8124 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FILM-REVIEW-CROWN-HNS     08-06 0966
