<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-06 13:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8136 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NEWSEDGE-LANG-ART-BOS     08-06 1472
