   &UR; NEW DNA TEST GIVES DOPE ON DEALERS &LR;  _ A new DNA-based test can
reveal if dope dealing suspects have been handling cannabis, just
by taking a swab from their hand. However, the test is so sensitive
there is a worry that innocent people could be incriminated. 550
words. By Joanna Marchant. Slugged:
BC-DOPE-ON-DEALERS-(NEW-SCIENTIST)-NYTSF) &QL;
