HEARST BUYS SAN FRANCISCO CHRONICLE 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDS: Version also moved in the ``a'' category)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 c. 1999 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
<P>
   SAN FRANCISCO _ The Hearst Corporation announced Friday that it
has agreed to buy the San Francisco Chronicle, a morning newspaper
published in the San Francisco Bay Area.
</P>
<P>
   The acquisition, which was for cash, includes ``SF Gate,'' the
