<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-06 19:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8630 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GOLAN-HEIGHTS-ART-NYT     08-06 0998
