-- Christina Hurr with her three boys: from left, John, 14, Greg,
16, and Matt, 14. ``Churches have prayer chains, but there is
nothing marketed to teens,'' says Ms. Hurr, 45, who has started the
Pray 4 Teens Ministry, where parents, friends or the teens
themselves can call or e-mail to request prayer support. (Jan
Underwood/Cox News Service Photo)
</P>
<P>
